# eng-team template manifest
#
# Paths listed here are MANAGED by the template and overwritten on every
# `scripts/sync-eng-team.sh` run. Anything not listed is project-local and
# never touched by sync.
#
# Rules:
#   - Paths are relative to the repo root.
#   - Trailing slash means "directory, recursive" (synced with --delete).
#   - No trailing slash means "single file".
#   - Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
#
# NOT MANAGED (for reference, never add these here):
#   - README.md                    (downstream projects have their own)
#   - .gitignore                   (project-specific)
#   - .claude/memory/              (project-local — see .claude/memory/README.md)
#   - .claude/settings.local.json  (local overrides)
#   - docs/sprints/[0-9]*          (active sprint folders)
#   - projects/                    (downstream project workspace)
#   - tools/                       (opt-in per project)
#   - scripts/bootstrap.sh         (template-only, runs once)

# Root-level managed files
CLAUDE.md
.eng-team.manifest

# Agent definitions
.claude/agents/

# Skill definitions
.claude/skills/

# Safety hooks
.claude/hooks/

# Helper scripts that ship with the template (e.g. API drift check)
.claude/scripts/

# Settings (hook registration). Use .claude/settings.local.json for project overrides.
.claude/settings.json

# Sprint templates + the sprint README
docs/sprints/_template/
docs/sprints/_template-hotfix/
docs/sprints/README.md

# Sync script itself (so `sync --self` can update it)
scripts/sync-eng-team.sh
